Package DynamicGraphGTU

Class MyGraph

java.lang.Object
DynamicGraphGTU.MyGraph
All Implemented Interfaces:
DynamicGraph, Graph
public class MyGraph extends Object implements DynamicGraph
An Adjancecy List graph implementation which uses Vertex class, it can grow and shrink dynamically.
